title: Pick Em Week 7 Featuring Team Lightswitch
description:
Team lightswitch is back and there is trouble and paradise! Lightswitch Lou may kill Shadow Matt and Big Cat and Hank dive into why. The boys also "break down" the weeks board and Matt makes his 5 team parlay of the week!!!
